data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath well-kept home located in a quiet close-knit Toccoa! The home features an open and bright floor plan with natural light and Great Views Toccoa. Plenty of room on 0.29 acres which is within walking distance of restaurants, shopping & recreation! Completely renovated less than 3 years ago, with a rocking chair front porch, fenced in back yard, new wood shed, & super quiet neighborhood! Must see to believe! EZ access to major highways! Good Schools!
